# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:5
msgid "Adaptation"
msgstr "改编"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:22
msgid ""
"The process of adjustment to actual or expected climate and its effects. In "
"human systems, adaptation seeks to moderate or avoid harm or exploit "
"beneficial opportunities. In some natural systems, human intervention may "
"facilitate adjustment to expected climate and its effects."
msgstr ""
"适应实际或预期气候及其影响的过程。在人类系统中，适应旨在缓和或避免伤害，或利用有益的机会。在某些自然系统中，人类干预可促进对预期气候及其影响的适应。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:8
msgid "Administrative unit"
msgstr "行政单位"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:25
msgid ""
"A geographic area that serves administrative and governmental functions. "
"They are usually defined and established by legal action."
msgstr "行使行政和政府职能的地理区域。它们通常是通过法律行动界定和建立的。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:11
msgid "Affected Area"
msgstr "受影响地区"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:28
msgid ""
"An arid, semi-arid and/or dry sub-humid area affected or threatened by "
"desertification"
msgstr "受荒漠化影响或威胁的干旱、半干旱和/或亚湿润干旱地区"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:14
msgid "Afforestation"
msgstr "植树造林"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:31
msgid ""
"Afforestation is planting of new forests on lands that historically have not"
" contained forests."
msgstr "植树造林是在历史上没有森林的土地上种植新的森林。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:17
msgid "Aggregation"
msgstr "汇总"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:34
msgid ""
"The combination of related categories, usually within a common branch of a "
"hierarchy, to provide information at a broader level to that at which "
"detailed observations are taken."
msgstr "相关类别的组合，通常是在一个层次结构的共同分支内，以提供更广泛层次的信息，而不是进行详细观察的层次。"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:20
#, python-format
msgid "Agriculture, value added (% of gross domestic product)"
msgstr "农业增加值（占国内生产总值的百分比）"

# Requires manual validation; translated with DeepL
#: ../../glossary.md:37
msgid ""
"One of the factors recommended to estimate the economic component of the "
"Drought Vulnerability Index (DVI). Agriculture corresponds to International "
"Standard Industrial Classifications (ISIC) divisions 1-5 and includes "
"forestry, hunting, and fishing, as well as cultivation of crops and "
"livestock production. This factor refers to the value added for agriculture "
"as a percentage of the gross value added at factor cost. It implies a higher"
" coping capacity of populations."
msgstr ""
"建议用于估算干旱脆弱性指数 (DVI) 经济部分的因素之一。农业与国际标准行业分类 (ISIC) 的 1-5 "
"类相对应，包括林业、狩猎和渔业，以及农作物种植和畜牧业生产。该系数指的是农业增加值占按要素成本计算的总增加值的百分比。这意味着人口的应对能力较强。"

